The @Jacobandco x @Alecmonopoly Timepiece Astronomia Alec Monopoly retails for $600,000 and is limited to 9 pieces 🔥💯 

The Astronomia Alec Monopoly contains miniature pop characters and images that are staples of Monopoly’s artwork within the iconic Astronomia four-arm vertical movement and its exclusive complications.

3-D 18K hand-engraved sculptures of Alec Monopoly's iconic characters in bright colors painted by the world renowned street artist.

node.text:
@JacobandCo Caviar Tourbillon blue Camouflage is so spectacularly flawless and a beautiful combination between the finest gemsetting and haute horlogerie 💎
Every component and every side of the 18K white gold case has to be specifically prepared to accommodate the exceptionally accurate cut stones to ensure a perfect fit - not once or twice, but over 800 times.
A coming together of haute Jewellery and haute horlogerie know-how like no other.⠀⠀
Fully set with 424 baguette-cut blue sapphires in varying hues to achieve the camo effect, this Caviar Tourbillon combines absolutely intense aesthetics with the haute de gamme gemsetting and watchmaking know-hows. 
This timepiece embodies the art of invisible gem setting. 👌🏼
Limited Edition to just 18 pieces worldwide 
⌚️tag price: $1,000,000.00

node.text:
The new residential Mega Yacht ‘Somnio’ will be the largest yacht in the world when it launches in 2024.

This 728 feet mansion will have 39 apartments across 6 floors, with apartment prices starting from $11,000,000 with an invite only to purchase. The cost of the project is to be around $600,000,000 and it will be built in Norway.
By: @winchdesign_wd

node.text:
Feeling lucky? @jacobandco Being the most creative watch company in the industry created the Astronomia Casino and will have you betting red or black with it’s fully operational minature roulette wheel.

The Astronomia Casino's wheel, rendered in a spectacular array of green, red, and black enamel with mahogany inlays, is set in motion by a button at the eight o'clock position (which also winds the power reserve for the animation).

This exceptional timepiece, the latest in @jacobandco signature Astronomia collection of celestial-themed timepieces, can be personalized with a mother of pearl insert placed by Jacob & Co. craftsmen on the owner's lucky number.
